  "name": "Impenetrable Scale",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Made of overlapping, lustrous black scales of standard-grade adamantine, this +2 greater resilient @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.8buhFcGwuaJRrp0y]{Fortification} adamantine scale mail seems to momentarily thicken at the point of impact when hit.</p>\n<p>Whenever the armor's fortification rune successfully turns a significant foe's critical hit into a normal hit, one of the scales on the armor turns violet. You gain resistance to physical damage equal to the number of violet scales, to a maximum of 8.</p>\n<p>At dawn each day, all the violet scales return to normal.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> The initial raw materials must include 1,600 gp of adamantine.</p>"
